        <span class="font-mono text-sm">/ khrotu</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mohan-yan-43905437b/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-white transition-colors group">
        <img src="/linkedin.svg" alt="LinkedIn" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" class="opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
        <span class="font-mono text-sm">/ me</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/blogs" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-white transition-colors group">
        <img src="/favicon-contrast.svg" alt="Blogs" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" class="opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
        <span class="font-mono text-sm">/ blogs</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <section class="flex flex-col gap-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <img
          src="/pfp.webp"
          alt="pfp, basically the minecraft lava bucket image but the l is flipped horizontally so it now reads java haha im so funny"
          width="96"
          height="96"
          fetchpriority="high"
          decoding="async"
          class="rounded-sm object-cover bg-neutral-800"
        />
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-medium text-[var(--text-main)]">
            KHROTU / khrotu / khrotubutms
          </h1>
          <a href="/name" class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-white transition-colors w-fit">
            what does that mean?
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed md:whitespace-nowrap">
          i'd like to think i'm a relatively competent dev; dabbles in ai/ml now and then
